# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:11
translate chinese u19a2s2c_7a270089:

    # "We walk north until the day turns to night and we're both tired and ready to make camp."
    "我们一路向北走，直到白昼转为黑夜，两人都累了，准备扎营。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:12
translate chinese u19a2s2c_74ad32c2:

    # "She helps me get a fire started and we eat some of the food my mom packed."
    "她帮我生起火，我们吃了些我妈妈准备的食物。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:19
translate chinese u19a2s2c_e134e96b:

    # cw "So you come from another world, where there's another me? What is she like?"
    cw "所以你是来自另一个世界，那里还有另一个我？她是什么样子的？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:20
translate chinese u19a2s2c_45c13b05:

    # pc "Similar... but different."
    pc "很像……但又不太一样。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:21
translate chinese u19a2s2c_09eee7ff:

    # cw "Like, how?"
    cw "比如，哪里不一样？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:23
translate chinese u19a2s2c_c4a12a39:

    # pc "Well, she doesn't have a spear and magic helmet... and Terry was just a guy, not a troll."
    pc "嗯，她没有长矛和魔法头盔……而且特里只是个普通人，不是巨魔。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:25
translate chinese u19a2s2c_382b0d8b:

    # cw "Ugh, there's a Terry there too?"
    cw "哎呀，那边也有个特里？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:27
translate chinese u19a2s2c_7d09960f:

    # pc "Yeah. She was kind of trapped by him and left him there too."
    pc "是啊。她当时被他困住了，最后也把他留在那儿了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:28
translate chinese u19a2s2c_d8746788:

    # pc "She's strong and smart and independent and everybody that meets her seems to like her."
    pc "她既强悍又聪明，还很独立，每个见到她的人似乎都很喜欢她。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:30
translate chinese u19a2s2c_a0c47e67:

    # cw "I guess she is kind of like me."
    cw "我想她确实有点像我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:31
translate chinese u19a2s2c_70cd19fd:

    # cw "Are you in love with her?"
    cw "你爱上她了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:33
translate chinese u19a2s2c_ba87bb2f:

    # pc "Yeah, I am."
    pc "是的，我爱上了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:35
translate chinese u19a2s2c_ab13114f:

    # cw "I understand why she would like you. You were very brave back there at the tower."
    cw "我明白她为什么会喜欢你。刚才在塔里，你表现得非常勇敢。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:36
translate chinese u19a2s2c_d07c1243:

    # pc "You did most of the work."
    pc "大部分都是你干的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:38
translate chinese u19a2s2c_e4c0d0d4:

    # cw "But I would still be chained to that wall if it wasn't for you."
    cw "但要不是你，我现在肯定还被锁在那面墙上。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:44
translate chinese u19a2s2c_100c64d5:

    # cw "So, thank you. I'm going to help you get your bracelet back and get back to your world."
    cw "所以，谢谢你。我会帮你拿回手镯，送你回你的世界。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:45
translate chinese u19a2s2c_84d1ad15:

    # cw "I know the other me must be missing you a lot."
    cw "我知道另一个我一定非常想念你。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:46
translate chinese u19a2s2c_e2b07877:

    # pc "Thanks, Dana."
    pc "谢谢，达娜。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:49
translate chinese u19a2s2c_701998d1:

    # cw "Right now, I need some sleep though. It's so nice being free again."
    cw "不过现在，我得睡会儿了。能重新获得自由真好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:50
translate chinese u19a2s2c_fa0eded1:

    # pc "How long did he have you imprisoned there?"
    pc "他把你关在那儿多久了？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:51
translate chinese u19a2s2c_5c54a582:

    # cw "I'm not sure. Years, I guess. I'm ready to forget it all and move on."
    cw "我不确定。大概有好几年吧。我已经准备好把这一切都抛在脑后，继续前行了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:54
translate chinese u19a2s2c_94849694:

    # pc "Are you going to just sleep on the ground?"
    pc "你打算直接睡在地上吗？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:55
translate chinese u19a2s2c_c2cc2961:

    # cw "Why not? It's great. I think I'm going to fall asleep very quickly."
    cw "为什么不呢？这样挺好的。我觉得我会很快睡着。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:58
translate chinese u19a2s2c_91f89767:

    # pc "Well, we can share my bedroll, if you feel like you want some extra padding or anything."
    pc "嗯，如果你觉得需要多点垫子什么的，我们可以共用我的睡袋。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:59
translate chinese u19a2s2c_b6397492:

    # cw "That's sweet of you, but I'm okay."
    cw "你真贴心，但我没关系。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:60
translate chinese u19a2s2c_00e51a40:

    # cw "Good night, [pcname]."
    cw "晚安，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:61
translate chinese u19a2s2c_db6f9f89:

    # pc "Good night, Dana."
    pc "晚安，达娜。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:62
translate chinese u19a2s2c_ef7b347d:

    # "I wonder if I'm going to be able to fall asleep tonight. I listen to the river and the noises of the woods and stare up into the sky."
    "不知道今晚我能不能睡着。我听着河水声和林间声响，仰望着天空。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:65
translate chinese u19a2s2c_cf11ff14:

    # "The stars look the same here. Brighter, maybe, but I still recognize the same constellations."
    "这里的星星看起来和以前一样。也许更亮了些，但我还是认出了那些熟悉的星座。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:66
translate chinese u19a2s2c_f964bb19:

    # "I wonder how much time has passed there. How everybody is doing. If they're panicking, looking for me."
    "不知道那边过去多久了。大家过得怎么样。会不会正慌张地四处找我。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:69
translate chinese u19a2s2c_dbecc6c1:

    # "I have to get back."
    "我必须回去。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:70
translate chinese u19a2s2c_198b9c05:

    # "I'm glad I have Dana here to help me, at least."
    "至少有达娜在这里帮我，我感到很庆幸。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:73
translate chinese u19a2s2c_6d353e62:

    # "Despite the new environment and lying on the hard ground, I am exhausted from all the walking and I fall asleep surprisingly quickly."
    "尽管身处陌生环境，又躺在坚硬的地面上，但长途跋涉让我筋疲力尽，我出乎意料地很快睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:76
translate chinese u19a2s2c_1e6eb085:

    # "In the morning, the sunlight shines down onto my face, waking me."
    "清晨，阳光洒在我的脸上，将我唤醒。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:77
translate chinese u19a2s2c_63ff8875:

    # "Dana is pressed up against me, her arm over my chest, her head lying on my shoulder."
    "达娜紧贴着我，手臂搭在我的胸口，头枕在我的肩上。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:78
translate chinese u19a2s2c_d1329dec:

    # "She feels so soft and warm, I hate to wake her, but we should get moving."
    "她摸起来如此柔软温暖，我真不忍心叫醒她，但我们该出发了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:79
translate chinese u19a2s2c_3070f281:

    # pc "Hey, Dana... time to wake up."
    pc "嘿，达娜……该起床了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:82
translate chinese u19a2s2c_5cf81d9d:

    # cw "Good morning."
    cw "早上好。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:83
translate chinese u19a2s2c_856a922e:

    # cw "You were right. The extra padding was nice."
    cw "你说的对。多层垫子睡起来真舒服。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:84
translate chinese u19a2s2c_c46a0b54:

    # pc "Any time."
    pc "不客气。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:87
translate chinese u19a2s2c_840a908b:

    # cw "Guess we better pack up and get going. Lots more walking to do to get you to the castle."
    cw "看来我们得收拾行装出发了。要带你到城堡，还有很长的路要走。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:90
translate chinese u19a2s2c_de8c2f3c:

    # "We pack up camp and continue walking north, both of us moving a little slower than we were the day before."
    "我们收拾好营地，继续向北行进，两人都比前一天走得慢了一些。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:93
translate chinese u19a2s2c_382298cc:

    # "Eventually, we reach another split in the road with no indication of where to go."
    "最终，我们来到另一处岔路口，没有任何路标指示该往哪走。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene2c.rpy:94
translate chinese u19a2s2c_c58944b7:

    # cw "Hm... what do you think?"
    cw "嗯……你觉得呢？"

